    "date": "2017-09-28T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Opioid Quota Openness, Transparency, and Awareness Act of 2017 or the Opioid QuOTA Act\n\nThis bill amends the Controlled Substances Act to require the Drug Enforcement Administration (DEA) to publish on its website certain information with respect to a registered manufacturer\u2019s opioid procurement quota.\n\nIt defines the term \"opioid procurement quota\" as a quota established by the DEA for the quantity of opioid analgesics that a registered manufacturer may procure."
